{
 "name": "RPlog_Operation_Shado_Kolpo_-_First_Wave",
 "title": "Operation Shado Kolpo: First Wave",
 "summary": "In the opening engagement of Operation Shado Kolpo, the New Republic 2nd Fleet's Task Force Zulu, led by Luke Skywalker in Jedi One and including Kyrin Sh'vani flying Ghost Four, escorts a freighter toward the Perlemian Route to break the Imperial blockade of Coruscant. They are intercepted by Imperial fighters under Krieg Inrokana, whose War Shrikes and TIE pilot Loki press a coordinated attack run on the freighter. A swirling dogfight unfolds, the Republic pilots straining to keep the TIEs off their charge while the Imperials score hits on its shields. When Corellian Gunships from the 2nd Fleet arrive in support, the outgunned Imperials disengage, and the battered but intact freighter survives its first wave of the operation.",
